4 Black & White Series booster packs
Sylveon and ALL the Eevee evolutions as special foil cards!

extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value: Kalos has been revealed, yet so much still remains unseen! New Trainers, new tactics, and the awe-inspiring Xerneas and Yveltal await - as does something else. Something...different. Something to make even the mightiest of Pokmon-EX tremble! A new age begins in the Pokmon TCG with Mega Evolution. Includes 2 all-new Mega Evolution Pokmon, 6 new Pokmon-EX, Pokmon TCG Online code cards. Over 140 cards in all!

results.cleanName: XY Base Set Theme Deck Resilient Life Xerneas

extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value:
A Strong Shield of Energy!
Resist, refuel, and retaliate with the Resilient Life theme deck. Xerneas can find Fairy Energy to recharge your Benched Pokemon, and Aromatisse moves that Energy around to wherever you need it most. Once your Pokmon have Fairy Energy attached, things get even better: Slurpuff's Sweet Veil Ability protects them from Special Conditions, and the Fairy Garden Stadium card lets them retreat for free! Flexible defenses are the key to your victory!

Contents:
1 60-card preconstructed deck
Damage counters
1 coin

results.name: XY Base Set Theme Deck - "Resilient Life" [Xerneas]

results.cleanName: XY Base Set Theme Deck Destruction Rush Yveltal

extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value:
A Swift Strike of Darkness!
Leave your opponents in the dust with the Destruction Rush theme deck! Yveltal retrieves lost Energy for a quick recovery with Oblivion Wing and wields the devastating Darkness Blade to great effect! Krookodile can Knock Back a battle-ready Pokemon to the Bench and keep powerful Supporter cards out of play. With Malamar's Mental Panic to keep your opponent's attacks at bay, retaliation won't be easyand the rush to destruction will be complete!

Contents:
1 60-card preconstructed deck
Damage counters
1 coin

results.name: XY Base Set Theme Deck - "Destruction Rush" [Yveltal]
